# Plantrail (agent-loop)

Use the plantrail workflow for non-trivial tasks:

- Create runs with `plantrail init-run --goal "..."`
- Complete `plan.md`, validate, review, then wait for user `plantrail approve <run> --by user`
- Log doing/decision/evidence to the active run
- Run `plantrail status` before risky actions; stop if hooks are not active

Reviewer agents may only write `review.md`. They cannot approve execution.
